original_title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup 3 (Night 3) (Grapes of Wrath)
overview: Not even the third annual Young Lions Cup can interrupt the pattern of "grape" themed named for our Pittston events. A 4-Corner Elimination tag bout is featured, alongside a wild relevos atomicos match. In an unforgettable tournament final, Icarus cements himself as the most-hated man in CHIKARA when he vies for the YLC opposite Shane Storm!
title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup 3 (Night 3) (Grapes of Wrath)
